org.aimas.craftingquest.state
Class CellState

java.lang.Object
  org.aimas.craftingquest.state.CellState
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class CellState
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable

Maintains the state of a map cell. It keeps data about the cell's type, position,
the lists of visible resources and objects,
the list of soil resources and of soil scan attributes,
the list of units and the strategicResource (if any) present in the cell.
